videos.headline: Arkansas' ball movement leads to a Makhi Mitchell dunk
videos.description: The Razorbacks move the ball around before finding Makhi Mitchell under the rim for an emphatic flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Arkansas' ball movement leads to a Makhi Mitchell dunk) 2023/01/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Colin Smith drains a tough 3
videos.description: Colin Smith drains a contested corner 3 and draws the foul for a 4-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Vanderbilt's Colin Smith drains a tough 3) 2023/01/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tempers flare between Arkansas and Vanderbilt
videos.description: A hard foul from Kamani Johnson leads to a heated exchange and technical foul on Johnson.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tempers flare between Arkansas and Vanderbilt) 2023/01/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Scuffle breaks out between Arkansas and Vanderbilt
videos.description: An and-1 finish by Anthony Black leads to a scuffle breaking out between the Razorbacks and the Commodores.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Scuffle breaks out between Arkansas and Vanderbilt) 2023/01/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vanderbilt pulls ahead off a Jordan Wright three
videos.description: Vanderbilt comes out strong with a 25-14 run to open the second half, capped off by a Jordan Wright three for the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Vanderbilt pulls ahead off a Jordan Wright three) 2023/01/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jerry Stackhouse gets tech after chucking his clipboard
videos.description: Vanderbilt's Ezra Manjon is ejected after a scuffle and Arkansas is awarded six free throws, leading to a Jerry Stackhouse technical.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jerry Stackhouse gets tech after chucking his clipboard) 2023/1/14 ESHEET
